{"tid":1845211,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【武漢肺炎】直擊政府倉庫存囤積最少90箱N95口罩 男子聞記者查問即大力關門","createTime":"2020-01-27T04:33:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-27T14:01:01.000Z","uid":85180,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"18c8bc6adfdf6a106a5ed0983f0038bc3590522c","tid":1845211,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:33:40.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】直擊政府倉庫存囤積最少90箱N95口罩 男子聞記者查問即大力關門<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discuss.com.hk/t/bd7d6b/f/800x0/https://appledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com/resizer/MuwGyKajJyJH5FIUalo3VCuRzUY=/720x405/arc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com/ap-ne-1-prod/public/NTJ7LWVLN6UQ7A7FVKJHMS2YFQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.discuss.com.hk%2Ft%2Fbd7d6b%2Ff%2F800x0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fappledaily-hk-appledaily-prod.cdn.arcpublishing.com%2Fresizer%2FMuwGyKajJyJH5FIUalo3VCuRzUY%3D%2F720x405%2Farc-photo-appledaily.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fap-ne-1-prod%2Fpublic%2FNTJ7LWVLN6UQ7A7FVKJHMS2YFQ.jpg&h=d00adb99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n高官連日來<br />\n都不肯呼籲市民戴口罩，特首林鄭月娥昨更惺惺作態稱會向中國國務院求助，要求供應國產口罩，但旋即被網民踢爆政府其實有逾億個口罩存貨。有讀者向《蘋果》爆料，指衞生署的倉庫仍有大量口罩封存，尚待出貨。記者上門叩門查詢，一名男子開門，聽罷記者問「呢度係唔係衞生署嘅口罩倉？」即大力關門，拒作回應。而就在他開門的數秒間，《蘋果》拍攝到倉內最少有2大塊卡板，每塊卡板擺放著最少45箱貨物；箱上的標籤列明「2130 N95 Respirator」，並有品牌「GERSON」標誌，相信是N95 口罩。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該大廈保安向記者承認，該貨倉隸屬衞生署，「積落好多口罩⋯⋯分啲畀市民，我就唔使周圍撲口罩喇！」沒戴口罩的他說。<br />\n查冊顯示，被指為衞生署口罩倉的工廠單位由冠榮有限公司持有，2013年起被政府全層租用，目前租約至2020年11月，每月租金10萬元。"},{"pid":"b24784352f9b7f9d6aa9f01e02174611f8ef6440","tid":1845211,"uid":85180,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:34:48.000Z","msg":"高官有口免費口罩用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e3cc0f91fc34c0bea4cb4570fca9699eb378e3d","tid":1845211,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:34:52.000Z","msg":"垃圾政府都推緊社福界去死！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1845195\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1845195</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AS4YPwC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAS4YPwC.jpg&h=a350fa60&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c6b3079d7fc16009905542f57db1f48e2c103a74","tid":1845211,"uid":85180,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:35:01.000Z","msg":"高官有免費口罩用了<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a9b6ff2fe1bebc26d86ff647058043e0bccaf23","tid":1845211,"uid":47080,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:39:10.000Z","msg":"高官有大量口罩炒了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n明明啲口罩係用納稅人錢買，都唔俾返香港市民"},{"pid":"fb4abc09362d7d457af216beecd6b16819513372","tid":1845211,"uid":19643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"n95留俾前線醫護仲好"},{"pid":"865be7de20f2e7ce647eea98cf3df1ce30df8c04","tid":1845211,"uid":24697,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"fb4abc09362d7d457af216beecd6b16819513372","tid":1845211,"uid":19643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"n95留俾前線醫護仲好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:44:07.000Z","msg":"N95不是俾市民用<br />\n唔好又on 9"},{"pid":"f52d3ab8fcbf4acf9d4261be6f5c94ff8154d061","tid":1845211,"uid":162015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T04:44:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e594943e76385743e8c3a91e0cbab1f193dc7734","tid":1845211,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:09:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c30e4a28764b017296f1ea91b125217e54c7752","tid":1845211,"uid":142007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-27T05:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":